Frontend (React):

Use Tailwind CSS or Material UI for design

Axios for API calls

React Query or SWR for data fetching

Responsive with media queries or utility classes


Backend (Express.js):

Routes: /api/auth, /api/user, /api/movies, /api/reviews

Middlewares: authMiddleware, errorHandler

Use dotenv, cors, helmet for config and security


Database (MongoDB):

Collections:

users: profile, email, favorites, watchlist

reviews: userId, movieId, rating, comment

(Optional) movies: if caching TMDB data



Movie API:

Use TMDB API with:

API Key in .env

Endpoints like /search/movie, /discover/movie, /movie/{id}




